data.description: Welcome to your DREAM HOME! This spacious and meticulously maintained ALL-BRICK 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom house is a true gem. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the pristine condition, modern features, and spacious open layout. This dream chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, where every detail has been meticulously crafted to elevate your cooking experience. From the sleek stainless-steel appliances to the ample granite countertops, this space is designed to empower your culinary creativity. Enjoy the thoughtful split floor plan that separates the owner's suite from the other bedrooms while perfectly balancing privacy and functionality. The owner's suite is the pinnacle of luxury living, a private oasis designed to pamper and rejuvenate your everyday experience. The spacious and inviting 5th bedroom, located upstairs, is the perfect retreat for your guests. With its comfortable furnishings, ample storage, and private en-suite bathroom, it's sure to make your visitors feel right at home. This house also boasts a stunning formal dining room, perfect for hosting memorable gatherings and creating cherished moments. Enjoy the serene backyard with an enclosed patio and lush landscaping. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is the epitome of modern living. Seize this incredible opportunity to make this recently built house your FOREVER HOME! Contact me today to arrange a viewing and experience the epitome of contemporary living in a house that's just waiting for you to call it yours.
